             WHERE pa.id IN (SELECT id FROM patients WHERE first='John' AND last='Doe') 
             AND p.code IN (SELECT code FROM procedures WHERE description='Mold (organism)') 
             ORDER BY p.description DESC 
             LIMIT 1;
